import { Routes as ReactRouterRoutes } from "react-router-dom";
import { Navigate } from "react-router-dom";

export const Routes = () => {
  return (
    <ReactRouterRoutes>
      {/* Pages */}
      <ReactRouterRoutes index element={<Presentation />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/dashboard/overview" element={<DashboardOverview />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/transactions" element={<Transactions />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/settings" element={<Settings />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/upgrade" element={<Upgrade />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/tables/bootstrap-tables" element={<BootstrapTables />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/billing" element={<Billing />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/invoice" element={<Invoice />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/sign-in" element={<Signin />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/sign-up" element={<Signup />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/forgot-password" element={<ForgotPassword />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/reset-password" element={<ResetPassword />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/lock" element={<Lock />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/404" element={<NotFound />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/examples/500" element={<ServerError />} />

      {/* Docs */}
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/documentation/overview" element={<DocsOverview />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/documentation/download" element={<DocsDownload />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/documentation/quick-start" element={<DocsQuickStart />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/documentation/license" element={<DocsLicense />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/documentation/folder-structure" element={<DocsFolderStructure />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/documentation/build-tools" element={<DocsBuild />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/documentation/changelog" element={<DocsChangelog />} />

      {/* Components */}
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/accordions" element={<Accordions />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/alerts" element={<Alerts />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/badges" element={<Badges />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/breadcrumbs" element={<Breadcrumbs />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/buttons" element={<Buttons />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/forms" element={<Forms />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/modals" element={<Modals />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/navs" element={<Navs />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/navbars" element={<Navbars />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/pagination" element={<Pagination />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/popovers" element={<Popovers />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/progress" element={<Progress />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/tables" element={<Tables />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/tabs" element={<Tabs />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/tooltips" element={<Tooltips />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/toasts" element={<Toasts />} />
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/components/widgets" element={<WidgetsComponent />} />

      {/* Widgets */}
      <ReactRouterRoutes path="/widgets" element={<Widgets />} />
    </ReactRouterRoutes>
  );
};
